    "reportNumber" : null,
    "citation" : "Sven Erik Avak, Margit Schwikowski, Anja Eichler. 2018. Impact and implications of meltwater percolation on trace element records observed in a high-Alpine ice core. Journal of Glaciology, 64(248), 877-886. doi: 10.1017/jog.2018.74",
    "type" : "publication",
    "identifier" : {
